'''Matt Jacobs''' (born [[July 1]], [[1950s#1956|1956]]) wrote the scripts for the game [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']] and the comic ''[[The Order of Outcasts]]'' in ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars Adventures Volume 5]]''. He had previously served as a writer for the [[Lucasfilm]] TV series [[Wikipedia:The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles|''The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles'']].

